%3e","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/0de42/me.jpg","srcSet":"/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/d7f6a/me.jpg 175w,\n/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/035d1/me.jpg 350w,\n/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/0de42/me.jpg 409w","srcWebp":"/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/07a3c/me.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/9fca7/me.webp 175w,\n/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/37a4e/me.webp 350w,\n/static/cb1103b5fa61dbaf4ba46515839215b8/07a3c/me.webp 409w","sizes":"(max-width: 409px) 100vw, 409px"}}},"skills":["HTML5 & CSS3","JavaScript","React","Vue","jQuery"]},"html":"<p>Hello! I'm Januar, a frontend developer based in Jakarta, who enjoys building things that live on the internet. I develop exceptional websites that provide intuitive, pixel-perfect user interfaces.</p>\n<p>Shortly after graduating from <a href=\"http://www.bsi.ac.id/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">BSI University</a> in 2014, I joined the B2B marketplace company at <a href=\"https://www.indotrading.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Indotrading</a> where I work on a wide variety of interesting and meaningful projects on a daily basis.</p>\n<p>Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Frontend Developer","company":"Alodokter","location":"Jakarta","range":"Jun 2019 - Present","url":"https://www.alodokter.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Translate of the UI/UX design wireframes to great code\nthat will produce visual elements of the application.</li>\n<li>Conduct research on methods or technologies related\nto front end website technology in hope to accelerate\nthe development of products/projects as well as\nenriching technology used in the company.</li>\n<li>Integrate and develop awesome front end features/systems, assuring their quality and running them in a\nproduction environment.</li>\n<li>Perform periodical tests and debugging to maximize\nprogram efficiency.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Frontend Developer","company":"Indonetwork","location":"Jakarta","range":"Jun 2018 - Jun 2019","url":"https://indonetwork.co.id/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Revamp old indonetwork design to drive business growth.</li>\n<li>Integrating API to build mobile apps using Vuejs.</li>\n<li>Develop new features using Vuejs on mobile apps android.</li>\n<li>Develop new features for desktop version and\nmobile responsive indonetwork. </li>\n<li>Create an html email template for indonetwork member.</li>\n<li>Optimize performance website blog.indonetwork.co.id.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Frontend Developer","company":"Indotrading","location":"Jakarta","range":"Nov 2015 - Jun 2017","url":"https://indotrading/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Develop and revamp a B2B website to drive\nbusiness growth.</li>\n<li>Build mobile m.indotrading.com for mobile responsive.</li>\n<li>Revamp the basic theme for members indotrading to\ndrive sales and visitors.</li>\n<li>Build landing page to explain indotrading products such\nas SEO, Premium, Google Ads.</li>\n<li>Build components that can be reused and\nfrontend libraries for the future.</li>\n<li>Revamp news.indotrading.com and optimize performance.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Web Designer","company":"Indotrading","location":"Jakarta","range":"Nov 2014 - Nov 2015","url":"https://indotrading.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Design a website based on Free and Premium member\npackages and convert to html responsive.</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Alodokter","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='225'%3e%3cpath%20d='M326%208v5h42V3h-42v5M0%2060v43h245l1-4v-4l1%203%201%204%201-4-1-5v-1l-1-1-1%202c0%205-5-8-6-16-1-12%201-16%2010-21l4-2%201%203c-1%202%200%208%201%2013%202%209%202%2010%20