ure Indonesia (IMI), is a company that was founded in 2009 and is a specialist company engaged in the Service Escalator and the replacement of Escalator Spare Parts and Elevators / Lifts.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Ma'had Syawarifiyyah","tech":["WordPress","WPBakery Page Builder","Custom Layout"],"github":"","external":"https://mahadsyawarifiyyah.com/"},"html":"<p>The official website of the Wahba An Nur Foundation (YWAN) Islamic Boarding School / Ma'had Syawarifiyyah (MSW) is on the Internet. This website aims to introduce Syawarifiyyah Islamic Boarding School (Ma'had) as an educational institution by utilizing internet technology media.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Izin Mudah","tech":["WordPress","WPBakery Page Builder","Custom Layout"],"github":"","external":"https://izinmudah.com/"},"html":"<p>izinmudah.com is present as a pioneer in terms of handling various licensing documents, company legality and manufacturing services of PT. We are here since 2001. From 2001 until now we have experienced and trusted licensing legal services.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Indotrading","tech":["ASP.NET","Bootstrap","jQuery","React"],"github":"","external":"https://indotrading.com/"},"html":"<p>Indotrading.com helps local B2B Business in Indonesia to have presence in Internet, boost their export sales, and maximize their sales.</p>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Get In Touch"},"html":"<p>Although I'm not currently looking for freelance opportunities, my inbox is always open. Whether for a potential project or just to say hi, I'll try my best to answer your email!</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":true}}}